Role-Based Booking & Appointment Platform
What This Platform Is

A service-based booking website where clients book appointments with providers for specific services, dates, and time slots. The system uses custom user roles so each user has access only to what they need.

What Can Be Booked

The platform supports booking services, not just time.

Examples of Bookable Services

Therapy sessions

Coaching calls

Business consultations

Barber or salon appointments

Fitness or yoga sessions

Nutrition consultations

Tutoring or mentoring sessions

Legal or financial consultations

Each service can have:

Duration (30, 45, 60 minutes)

Price (optional)

Session type (online or in-person)

Description

How Booking Works (User Flow)
Client Flow

Sign up / log in as a client

Browse providers or services

Select a service

Choose an available date & time

Confirm booking

Receive email confirmation

View booking history and upcoming sessions

Provider Flow

Create a professional profile

Define services they offer

Set working hours and availability

Block unavailable dates

View upcoming and past bookings

Receive booking notifications

Admin Flow

Manage all users and roles

Approve providers

Manage service categories

View all bookings

Configure email notifications and booking rules

Booking Logic & Rules

Real-time availability checks

No overlapping appointments

Automatic time-slot generation

Booking cutoff rules (e.g., cannot book within 2 hours)

Cancellation/reschedule policies

Optional payment integration

Design & UX

Clean, calming, professional layout

Step-by-step booking process

Minimal form fields

Clear CTAs (Book Now, Confirm Appointment)

Mobile-first design

Why Employers & Clients Love This

Solves a real business problem

Shows full-stack thinking (logic + UX)

Custom roles demonstrate backend skills

Easy to extend into a SaaS product

Works across many industries

Optional Enhancements

Google Calendar sync

Zoom / Google Meet links for online sessions

Automated reminders

Reviews & ratings for providers

Multi-location support